Here’s the HTML rewritten with an energetic gaming community tone: direct, exciting, and emoji-friendly.
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>StatForge 🔥 Warframe DPS</title>
